Run an accelerator validation

Validate that an accelerator meets minimum thresholds of quality. This process will scan all of the artifacts associated with an accelerator, which may be packaged in Update Sets, Scopes or Plugins, ensuring that best practices are followed, and generating both risk and risk mitigation metrics. The risk & mitigation metrics will be compared to standard criteria in order to make the final Pass/Fail validation judgement. All of the information collected and generated will be stored in a validation metrics record, along with the validation status.
